//Heart valves/Outflow tract - Aortic valve


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 04 of Cardio MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
When I select 'Heart valves/Outflow tract' tab
Then 'Heart valves' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'RVOT obstruction' checkbox is enabled
And 'LVOT obstruction' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'LVOT obstruction' checkbox
Then 'At rest' radio button is enabled
And 'With Valsalva' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Aortic valve' from 'Heart valves' dropdown menu
Then 'Add pathology' button is enabled
And 'Stenosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Insufficiency' checkbox is enabled
And 'Calcification' checkbox is enabled
And 'Variant' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Stenosis' checkbox
Then 'Quantification' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Insufficiency' checkbox
Then 'Quantification' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Variant' checkbox
Then 'Quadricuspid valve' radio button is enabled
And 'Bicuspid valve' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Bicuspid valve' radio button
Then 'Type' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Phenotype' dropdown menu is enabled
